P(k+1)
 \sum_{i=1}^k i\cdot i! = (k+1)! - 1
 \sum_{i=1}^{k+1} i\cdot i! = ((k+1)+1)! - 1\\ \sum_{i=1}^{k+1} i\cdot i! = (k+2)! - 1
