 \sum_{i=1}^ni\cdot i!=\sum_{i=1}^n(i+1-1)\cdot i!=\sum_{i=1}^n(i+1)\cdot i!-1\cdot i! 
 =\sum_{i=1}^n (i+1)!-i!=(n+1)!-n!+n!-\ldots-2!+2!-1!=(n+1)!-1. 
